name: Five nights at bönan. (fan made fnaf game) v.1.1.0
name_original: Five nights at bönan. (fan made fnaf game) v.1.1.0
description:
WHATS NEW!? what is new in the latest v.1.1.0 update :D

I MADE katt-räven A LITTLE DARKER AND MADE HIM SCARIER WHEN HES ABOUT TO ATTACK!

I CHANGED SO THAT den gröna emo chillin GETS CORRUPTED IN WHEN HE YOU KNOW LAGS IN HARDER NIGHTS

I ADDED A NEW JUMPSCARE TO bönan BEACUSE I FROGOT TO DO THAT SO FREDDY WOULD APPEAR INSTEAD.

I ADDED A JUMPSCARE FOR golden bönan BEACUSE I FROGOT THAT TOO (golden freddy would appear instead)

YOU NO LONGER NEED TO COMPLEATE NIGHT 6 TO BE ABLE TO PLAY COSTOM NIGHT.

NIGHT 6 IS AVILIBLE WHENEVER YOU WANT

YOU WILL SE A DIFFICULTY AT THE BEGGINING OF ALL NIGHTS

ADDED LOADING SCREEN

MADE MENU MUSIC DARKER

ADDED NEW GIGGLE WHEN golden bönan APPEARS

(reminder this game is swedish)

Böna = bean

katt-räven = the cat fox

groöna emo chillin = the grren emo chili

svampen = The mushroom
